00:03:04,147 --&gt; 00:03:02,333
I want to win for baby and child.

00:03:02.333 --> 00:03:09.555
I think convincing Matsumoto to give K-1 up and getting a regular job,

00:03:09.555 --> 00:03:13.819
The star of the show.

00:03:13.819 --> 00:03:17.123
The man hoping to steal that star.

